    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Professional Background</h2>
        <p>
          As a Senior Data Scientist at BP with extensive experience in the oil
          and gas industry, I specialize in developing and deploying machine
          learning solutions that enhance operational efficiency and reduce
          downtime. My work spans the full data science lifecycle‚Äîfrom
          stakeholder engagement and requirements gathering to model deployment,
          monitoring, and mentoring junior team members.
        </p>
        <p>
          My most significant achievement is leading the development of a
          patent-pending methodology for time series anomaly detection, which
          represents a novel approach to identifying operational issues before
          they impact production. This work demonstrates my ability to innovate
          beyond traditional statistical methods and create practical solutions
          for complex industrial challenges.
        </p>
        <p>
          What sets me apart as a data scientist is my full-stack approach‚ÄîI'm
          not just focused on the statistical modeling side, but also deeply
          involved in the entire pipeline from data cleaning and evaluation to
          cloud deployment and stakeholder communication. This comprehensive
          perspective allows me to bridge the gap between technical complexity
          and business value, ensuring that models deliver real-world impact.
        </p>
